import Gallery from "@components/Gallery.astro";
---

<section class="container mb-12">
    <h2>
        The decision that changed my life:
    </h2>
    <p>
        After realizing I was working too much and was not happy with where my life was heading, I decided to
        move to Dublin, Ireland, to improve my English and chase new experiences. That journey changed me in
        ways I didn't expect.
    </p>
    <ul class="mb-12">
        <li>
            My English improved dramatically.
        </li>
        <li>
            I met wonderful people from all over the world and learned from very different cultures.
        </li>
        <li>
            I got to know myself better — what I value, what drains me, and what I actually want out of life.
        </li>
        <li>
            I traveled across Europe whenever I could.
        </li>
        <li>
            I joined <b><a target="_blank" href="https://www.codu.co/">Codú</a></b>, a developer community in Dublin.
        </li>
        <li>
            I discovered how much I enjoy teaching and sharing what I know.
        </li>
        <li>
            I fell in love with the mountains.
        </li>
    </ul>
    <Gallery/>
</section>